13 February 2015 Government will hold cluster media briefings on the implementation of the Government Programme of Action for 2015 post the State of the Nation Address.The briefings are scheduled as follows:Sunday, 15 February 2015 10h00- 11h00: International Cooperation, Trade and Security (ICTS) Cluster chaired by Minister of Telecomunications and Postal Services, Siyabonga CweleVenue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town.NB : Via link up to GCIS Head Office, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard Street, Hatfield, Pretoria 11h00- 13h00 Social Protection, Community and Human Development Cluster chaired by Minister of Social Development, Bathabile DlaminiVenue: GCIS Head Office, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard Street, Hatfield,NB : Via link up to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town.RSPV: Themba Thobela (Pretoria) Cell: 076 09 56555 E-mail: Thembat@doc.gov.zaMzimasi Ngqelu (Cape Town) Cell: 076 904 3557 E-mail: Mzi@gcis.gov.za Tuesday, 17 February 2015 8h30- 10h30 Governance and Administration ( G&amp;A) Cluster chaired by Minister of Home Affairs, Malusi GigabaVenue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town.NB : Via link up to GCIS Head Office, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard Street, Hatfield, Pretoria Thursday, 19 February 2015 8h30- 10h30 Justice Crime Prevention and Security Cluster chaired by Minister of Defence and Military Veterans, Nosiviwe Mapisa-NqakulaVenue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town.NB : Via link up to GCIS Head Office, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard Street, Hatfield, Pretoria RSVP: Ireen Magwai ( Pretoria) Cell: 082 440 5676Mzimasi Ngqelu (Cape Town) Cell: 076 904 3557 E-mail: Mzi@gcis.gov.zaEnquiries: Nikelwa Tengimfene (International Cooperation Trade and Security and Justice Crime Prevention and Security Cluster Supervisor) Cell: 082 574 5495Legadima Leso (Social Protection, Community and Human Development and Governance a